taxon.name: Amara

default_photo.attribution: (c) gernotkunz, all rights reserved, uploaded by gernotkunz

taxon.wikipedia_summary: Amara is a large genus of carabid beetles, commonly called the sun beetles. Many are holarctic, but a few species are neotropical or occur in eastern Asia.

results.place_guess: Pepper Tree Ln, Los Gatos, CA, US
